This proof establishes a circle of equivalence: From { ~ impsingle }, { ~ ax-1 , ~ imim1 , ~ peirce } was proved. From { ~ ax-1 , ~ imim1 , ~ peirce }, { ~ ax-1 , ~ ax-2 and ~ peirce } was proved.
